Title: Eyes of the Weaver
Description:
The Weaver's many eyes lurk throughout the city, learning as much as they can about Ansurek's machinations.

Still, intelligence enough will not be sufficient to turn the tide against the Sureki forces. The Weaver requires someone willing to get their hands dirty.

Lucky you, I suppose.
ObjectivesText: Continue your efforts in aiding the Weaver in Azj-Kahet.
RewardText:
You have big talent for causing good trouble! Good good!

Take these!

Objectives.Text: View Yamas the Provider's Pact items
